rows.label: qst202604_msg0001
rows.name:
We have conquered the enemy,
Your Majesty. You need fear no
longer.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0002
rows.name:
Truly, I am grateful to you, from the
bottom of my heart.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0003
rows.name:
Where are all these monsters coming
from, though?

rows.label: qst202604_msg0004
rows.name:
First Luxuria, now here...
It's certainly a cause for concern.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0005
rows.name:
The introduction of foreign species
to endemic regions could wildly
disrupt their ecosystems.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0006
rows.name:
We've already identified where
the Laias are coming from.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0007
rows.name: Really?!

rows.label: qst202604_msg0008
rows.name:
Yes, a messenger from Temperantia
arrived while you were out fighting.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0009
rows.name:
Laias appear to have been spawning at
an alarming rate at a place called
Xataris Spring in Temperantia.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0010
rows.name: Temperantia, eh?

rows.label: qst202604_msg0011
rows.name:
So they're born in Temperantia and
then migrate to other Divine Beasts by air...

rows.label: qst202604_msg0012
rows.name:
So they could be causing trouble in
other countries too? This is bad...

rows.label: qst202604_msg0021
rows.name:
Indeed. It seems that to address the
heart of the matter, we'll have to rid
Temperantia of its Laias.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0022
rows.name:
Going up against those things isn't
half exhausting, though...

rows.label: qst202604_msg0023
rows.name:
But we have to do this.
No one else can!

rows.label: qst202604_msg0024
rows.name: True enough. Shall we, then?

rows.label: qst202604_msg0025
rows.name:
Sorry Ten'i, looks like our job's
still not over yet.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0026
rows.name: That is fine by me...

rows.label: qst202604_msg0027
rows.name:
The future of Alst is in your hands.
My thoughts go with you.

rows.label: qst202604_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]...!

rows.label: qst202604_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]What...?
What is this strange feeling...?

rows.label: qst202604_msg0016
rows.name: Don't tell me my power is...

rows.label: qst202604_msg0017
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Hey, Ten'i! We're leaving!

rows.label: qst202604_msg0018
rows.name: Ah, yes! Coming!
